entries.complete: Navigation droid: < Scan of intact data among debris indicate origin, labor outpost, moon 4 of Yavin. >
entries.title: Dantooine system: Defeat the ambush.
entries.title_d: Ogveer tricked you. Defeat the ambush that he lead you in to. Maybe a scan of the pirates floating debris might reveal some clues. Keep close attention to messages from your droid unit.
